\s1 Burying criminals
\pi. ?i I , I I , | ,m,,,li I,,
\v 22 If someone is executed for having committed a crime for which he deserves to die, and you hang his corpse on a post,
\v 23 you must not allow his corpse to remain there all night. You must bury it on the day that he died, because if you keepthe corpse on a post, God will curse the land. \add You must bury the corpse thatday\add*, in order that you do not defile the land that Yahweh our God is giving to you.”